Package ml

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Driver
    Driver class to run ML related tasks
    FeatureExtractor
    Class to facilitate the extraction of features from an email in order to produce an input for the Machine Learning models.
    FeatureExtractorTest  
    FeatureWriter
    Static class to write the results of Feature extraction to a file.
    MboxParser
    Class to read in emails from a .mbox file.
    NeuralNets
    Class to facilitate obtaining data from files and training a neural classifier.
    TrainResults
    Class to store training results from cross-validation.
